    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of an Algonquian-speaking Native American tribe located in Long Island, New York. Have also been referred to as the "Poospatuck" in reference to the reservation the Unkechaug live on (Poospatuck Reservation, NY). </Note_Text>
